<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Thank you for your order, <%= @customer.surname %>!</h2>
    <p>
      You have successfully purchased
      <%= pluralize(@ordered_item.quantity, @ordered_item.item.quantity_unit) %> of
      <%= @ordered_item.item.name.pluralize(@ordered_item.quantity) %>
      (Total <%= @ordered_item.item.price * @ordered_item.quantity %> <%= @ordered_item.item.currency %>)!


      If you made this order by a mistake, you should
      be able to cancel it at your order-overview <%= link_to 'here', ordered_items_url %>.
      At the overview you can always check the status of your orders too!

      Of course you wouldn't be able to cancel your order, if the item has already been shiped!
    </p>

    <p>

      Please do not hesitate to contact <a href="mailto:railsshoptest@gmail.com">railsshoptest@gmail.com</a>
      if you have any further questions.
    </p>
    <p>Yours sincerely
    RailsShop</p>
  </body>
</html>
